data.description: Introducing your ideal family home at 9909 Nixon Drive, McKinney, TX 75002 – A meticulously maintained 4-bedroom, 3-bath residence nestled in the charming neighborhood of Eagles Nest At Westridge. This home offers an open concept design, creating a welcoming and expansive feel, with a generously sized game room for family entertainment. Located within walking distance to the community pool, splash pad, schools, parks, and picturesque tree-lined walking and jogging trails, it seamlessly combines convenience and a vibrant community lifestyle. With clean and well-kept interiors, it's a move-in ready haven, recent updates include a new 30-year shingle roof, engineered wood flooring, fresh carpet, and exterior and interior paint. Perfect for making lasting memories with your loved ones in the heart of sought-after McKinney, TX!
